$
  E = integral_(‚ĄĚ^3) #d x (T^0_0) 
  = integral_(‚ĄĚ^3) #d x ((‚ĄŹ^2)/(2m) |‚ąā_x Ōą|^2)
$
Due to the zero divergence of the energy-momentum tensor, energy is conserved with respect to time $t$, $‚ąā_t E = 0$

