The spatial part of the current is similar to the relativistic case, $(‚ĄŹ^2)/(2m) (Ōą^* ‚ąā_x Ōą - Ōą ‚ąā_x Ōą^*) = (‚ĄŹ^2)/(m) Im(Ōą^* ‚ąā_x Ōą)$

